<C>__{pk}
<D>__{i didn't mean to tell you what you can and can't talk about back in the cave today. i guess i just don't like to think of you being...}
<P>__{(beat)}
<C>__{pk }
<D>__{... becoming...}
<P>__{(beat)}
<D>__{... something else. i know it's natural law and it's the way it is with everybody...}
