<C>__{pk}
<D>__{doc?}
<A>__{pk turns to doc, dead asleep, still sitting up. pk goes over and gently lays the old man down. he removes his boots and throws a blanket over him. pk blows out the kerosene lamp and goes to exit. he is about to hang their two rucksacks on two hooks by the door when doc's voice turns him.}
