<D>__{the heart.}
<A>__{he is asleep when his head hits the pillow. pk watches doc's chest, washed in moonlight, rise and fall lightly. a sudden sadness falls over him. the corners of his mouth turn up in a bittersweet smile. he finishes hanging the rucksack and exits.}
